title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 250
description:
The 2015 Rigmar Radio Karaoke collection 250 Songs in a single WinRAR Archive, also included is some files to help those new to bit torrent who may have difficulty downloading each part in the 24 hours seeding window.

A full track listing will be published in plain text and CSV formats for the making of a Karaoke song suggestion book.

Please do not run more than one torrent if your download speed is very poor.

This is a large download 1.5GB in size.  The songs are in CDG+MP3 format.

The Whole collection is over 51,000 songs and will take about 300GB space and will be uploaded 250 songs at a time every 24 hours.   It is up to the community to seed each part after that 24 hour window has passed.  The collection is international and contains French, Spanish, Maltese, Italian, Swedish and German Karaoke tracks as well as English.  It has been purchased over many years both in North America as well as Europe.   Enjoy.. Oh the counter 500 tells you how far along you are.  When it reaches 50,000 you have not got long to go tee hee...  Enjoy!
